    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">scoped</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Topology</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Pointwise</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">SeminormedAddCommGroup</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">NormedSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">â„</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">U</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ğ“</span><span class=\"bp\">Ë¢</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">U</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">â‰¤</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ğ“</span><span class=\"bp\">Ë¢</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">U</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ğ“</span><span class=\"bp\">Ë¢</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- let W be any set in N(U)+N(V)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">W</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hW</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- by definition</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- let A, B be sets with U âŠ† interior(A), V âŠ† interior(B), and A + B âŠ† W</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">obtain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">âŸ¨</span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hA</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hB</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"bp\">âŸ©</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hW</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- let U' and V' be opens with U âŠ† U' âŠ† A and V âŠ† V' âŠ† B</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_nhdsSet_iff_exists</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hA</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hB</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">obtain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">âŸ¨</span><span class=\"n\">U'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hU'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hUU'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">HU'A</span><span class=\"bp\">âŸ©</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hA</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">obtain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">âŸ¨</span><span class=\"n\">V'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hV'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hVV'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hV'B</span><span class=\"bp\">âŸ©</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hB</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- we want to find some open W' with U + V âŠ† W' âŠ† W</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_nhdsSet_iff_exists</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- We claim U' + V' works</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">U'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V'</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- is an open set with U + V âŠ† U' + V' âŠ† W</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- so we now need to check it's open, it contains U+V and it's contained in W</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">refine</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">âŸ¨?_</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">?_</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">?_âŸ©</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">Â·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">-- U' + V' is open because it's a union of open sets (translate of V')</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IsOpen</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">add_left</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hV'</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">Â·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">-- the inclusion U + V âŠ† U' + V' is clear by monotonicity results</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">mono</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">Â·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">-- and the inclusion U' + V' âŠ† W is also clear</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">subset_trans</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">show</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">U'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">âŠ†</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mono</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>is the inclusion which we have the proof of.</p>",
